message: While this is a milestone in trying to end exploitation of children, Backpage getting shut down will not stop Sex Trafficking. International Labor Organization (ILO) reported in 2014 there were $99 Billion in profits from commercial sexual exploitation.  Traffickers will find other avenues to exploit victims.  Education and Awareness is needed now more than ever! #Backpage
